---
import Container from '@components/container.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Education Operations Pro Group Accountability">
	<main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Elevate Your Education Business with Pro Group Accountability</h1>
		
		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Our Mission</h2>
			<p>Join our exclusive group of education business owners and operators to skyrocket your performance for just $400/month. We're committed to helping you optimize your operations, increase enrollment, and boost profitability through accountability and peer support.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. The Challenge</h2>
			<p>Education business owners often face unique obstacles:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
				<li>Balancing educational quality with business profitability</li>
				<li>Managing fluctuating enrollment and revenue</li>
				<li>Keeping up with evolving educational technologies and methodologies</li>
				<li>Navigating complex regulations and compliance requirements</li>
				<li>Difficulty in measuring and improving key performance indicators (KPIs)</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Our Solution</h2>
			<p>Our Pro Group Accountability program for education operations addresses these challenges by providing:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
				<li>Weekly accountability meetings with fellow education business owners</li>
				<li>Customized KPI tracking dashboard for education businesses</li>
				<li>Access to a network of experienced education entrepreneurs</li>
				<li>Exclusive resources on education business management and growth strategies</li>
				<li>Regular workshops on topics like student retention, marketing, and operational efficiency</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. How It Works</h2>
			<p>Our program is designed to keep your education business on track and growing:</p>
			<ol class="list-decimal list-inside ml-4">
				<li>Set your education business goals and KPIs</li>
				<li>Attend weekly group accountability sessions with other education entrepreneurs</li>
				<li>Track your progress using our custom education business dashboard</li>
				<li>Share insights and overcome challenges with peer support</li>
				<li>Implement best practices and celebrate milestones together</li>
			</ol>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Pricing</h2>
			<p>Invest in your education business's success with our Pro Group Membership:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
				<li>Monthly fee: <strong>$400</strong></li>
                <li>Weekly meetings every Monday at 10:30am</li>
				<li>No long-term contracts - cancel anytime</li>
				<li>100% satisfaction guarantee</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

