		<section>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Join Now</h2>
			<p>Ready to take your education business to the next level? Join our Pro Group Accountability program today!</p>
			<button class="bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-6 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300 mt-4">Sign Up Now</button>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>